-- Canada Panel Approves Exxon’s C$16 Billion Mackenzie Gas Line
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   D o n v i l l e
-- 2010-12-16T21:37:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/canada-panel-approves-exxon-s-proposed-16-billion-mackenzie-gas-pipeline.html
Exxon’s C$16 billion Mackenzie gas
pipeline was approved by Canada’s National Energy Board,
depending on the company meeting more than 200 conditions and
starting construction by 2015.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Donville in Vancouver at 
 cjdonville@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
